title: Today in History: FEB 4, Rosa Parks is born
description:
Today in History

Today is Saturday, Feb. 4, the 35th day of 2023. There are 330 days left in the year. 

Today’s Highlight in History: 

On Feb. 4, 1783, Britain’s King George III proclaimed a formal cessation of hostilities in the American Revolutionary War…
author: The Associated Press
